---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import UKStatistics from '../components/UKStatistics';
import { BarChart3, TrendingUp, MapPin, AlertTriangle, Clock, Smartphone, ArrowRight } from 'lucide-react';
---

<Layout 
  title="UK Mobile Theft Statistics & Trends | ProtectMyMobile"
  description="Comprehensive statistics and data on mobile phone theft across the UK including hotspots, trends, recovery rates, and time-of-day analysis."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="bg-[#f3f2f1]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-7xl">
      
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-neutral-900">UK Mobile Theft Statistics</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 max-w-3xl">
          Real data and insights on mobile phone theft trends across the United Kingdom. 
          Updated with the latest available data from UK police forces and ONS.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Key Metrics - Interactive Component -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <UKStatistics client:load />
      </section>
      
      <!-- Time of Day Analysis -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">When Do Thefts Occur?</h2>
              <p class="text-neutral-600">Time-of-day breakdown shows when you're most at risk (UK National Average)</p>
            </div>
            <Clock class="h-12 w-12 text-primary" />
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <span class="text-lg font-semibold">Evening Rush Hour</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500">(5pm - 7pm)</span>
                </div>
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600">32%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="w-full bg-neutral-200 rounded-full h-6 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-red-600 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-end pr-3" style="width: 32%">
                  <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">Highest Risk</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-2">Peak time on public transport, busy streets, distracted commuters</p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <span class="text-lg font-semibold">Late Night</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500">(10pm - 2am)</span>
                </div>
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-600">28%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="w-full bg-neutral-200 rounded-full h-6 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-600 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-end pr-3" style="width: 28%">
                  <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">High Risk</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-2">Nightlife areas, reduced awareness, fewer witnesses</p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <span class="text-lg font-semibold">Morning Rush Hour</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500">(7am - 9am)</span>
                </div>
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-600">18%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="w-full bg-neutral-200 rounded-full h-6 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 to-yellow-600 h-6 rounded-full" style="width: 18%"></div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-2">Busy commutes, crowded transport, quick snatch opportunities</p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <span class="text-lg font-semibold">Afternoon</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500">(12pm - 5pm)</span>
                </div>
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">15%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="w-full bg-neutral-200 rounded-full h-6 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 h-6 rounded-full" style="width: 15%"></div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-2">Shopping areas, cafes, tourist spots</p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <span class="text-lg font-semibold">Other Times</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500">(2am - 7am, 9am - 12pm)</span>
                </div>
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-600">7%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="w-full bg-neutral-200 rounded-full h-6 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-neutral-500 to-neutral-600 h-6 rounded-full" style="width: 7%"></div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-2">Lower activity periods, fewer thefts reported</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-sm text-yellow-900">
              <strong>⚠️ Stay Alert During Peak Times:</strong> Be extra vigilant with your phone during evening rush hour and late at night. 
              Keep devices secure, use inside pockets, and be aware of your surroundings.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <!-- Interactive Timelapse CTA - Enhanced -->
      <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-12 text-white text-center mb-12">
        <MapPin class="h-16 w-16 mx-auto mb-6 opacity-90" />
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Explore Interactive Theft Hotspots</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-purple-100 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          See exactly where and when thefts occur with our interactive timelapse map. 
          Watch patterns emerge over time and identify high-risk areas near you.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/timelapse" 
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-purple-600 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors shadow-lg"
        >
          View Timelapse Map <ArrowRight class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" />
        </a>
      </section>

      <!-- Additional Context -->
      <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Why These Numbers Matter</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-neutral-700">
            <p>
              <strong>Beyond the device:</strong> Mobile theft isn't just about losing hardware. Victims face identity theft, financial fraud, loss of irreplaceable photos, and significant emotional distress.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Recovery is rare:</strong> With only 1.7% of cases resulting in charges across the UK, prevention and immediate response are crucial.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Growing problem:</strong> The 15% national increase (and higher in major cities) shows this is an escalating issue requiring better awareness and protection.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">What You Can Do</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <a href="/prevention" class="block p-4 bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
              <div class="font-semibold text-primary mb-1">Protect Your Device</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Set up security features before theft occurs</div>
            </a>
            <a href="/emergency" class="block p-4 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-100 transition-colors">
              <div class="font-semibold text-red-700 mb-1">Know What to Do</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Have an emergency response plan ready</div>
            </a>
            <a href="/banks" class="block p-4 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-100 transition-colors">
              <div class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-1">Save Key Contacts</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Have bank and provider numbers ready</div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
